Fantastic Beasts And When To Find Them is a movie based on the a spin-off novel written by award winning author J.K. Rowling of the same title that was released in 2016. The movie followed the story of a new character called Newt Scamander– played by Eddie Redmayne– who arrived in 1926 New York with a briefcase of magical creatures. Events unfold and the creatures escape leading Newt on a unexpected adventure with new friends. A sequel to the movie drops later this year and the official trailer is finally here. 